==Russian==
===Etymology===
Deliberate misspelling of '''[[в]] [[топка|топку]]''', literally ''into the [[furnace]]''.

===Idiom===
'''фтопку!''' (ftópku) 
#(''as [[imperative]]'') [[Burn]] it! [[Delete]] it!

===Usage note===
Popular Internet slang expression. It belongs to the so-called [[:w:Padonki|Padonki]] slang ([[жаргон]] [[подонки|падонков]]). Presumably '''фтопку''' originated as a cynical allusion to the [[crematory|crematories]] of the Nazi extermination camps.

